 "blurb": "Survival Hunter is a raid multiplier: Expose Weakness procs grant the whole melee/hunter core attack power scaled off your agility. Personal DPS is the lowest of the three trees; the raid total says otherwise, and the gear list stacks agility beyond what any other hunter would. This Phase 3 snapshot aggregates 240 top DPS parses from Black Temple and Mount Hyjal; the highest-consensus pick is Telonicus' Pendant of Mayhem at 87% usage.",
 "statPriorityRationale": "Expose Weakness converts your agility into attack power for every physical DPS in the raid — survival is the only spec whose primary stat multiplies across ten other players, so agility leads even before the hit cap.",
